text: Edward James Nestor was a cyclist from Australia. Edward competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and 1956 Summer Olympics. He was born on 12 January 1920 and died on 16 June 2010.Jim Nestor == References == Category:1920 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Australian cyclists Category:Olympians for Australia Category:Sportspeople from South Australia
